HEADWORD: Dumpish
<hw>Dump"ish</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Dull; stupid; sad; moping;
melancholy.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧ A . . . <xex>dumpish</xex> and sour
life.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Lord Herbert.</au></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Dump"ish*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Dump"ish*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

